name: Weequay Hunter
Lore: 'To maintain religious practices, Weequay hunters capture banthas. The beasts are then sacrificed as part of a battle ceremony. Tusken Raiders tend not to appreciate this.',
Text: 'Deploys only on Tatooine. When present at the start of a battle, may sacrifice (lose) one of your Banthas present: adds 2 to power of each Weequay there for remainder of turn. (May not sacrifice if Tusken Raiders present outnumber Weequay present).',
